OL,3,C'Shocking' rise in dog cruelty
OL,4,Creports, says RSPCA
OL,6,FAn animal welfare charity has said it
OL,7,Fhas seen a "shocking" rise in dog
OL,8,Fcruelty cases across the South West.
OL,10,FThe RSPCA received 1,659 reports of
OL,11,Fcruelty to dogs in Devon and Cornwall
OL,12,Fin 2023, compared with 1,485 in 2022 -
OL,13,Fan increase of more than 11%.
OL,15,FSammy Thompson, marketing and
OL,16,Ffundraising manager at RSPCA Cornwall
OL,17,FBranch, said: "We can't believe there
OL,18,Fhas been a rise in dog cruelty cases.
