OL,3,C'Shocking' rise in dog cruelty
OL,4,Creports, says RSPCA
OL,6,F"And it's not just beatings, it's
OL,7,Fstabbings, it's mutilations - it's
OL,8,Fhorrendous things that we can't get
OL,9,Four heads around."
OL,11,FThe number of reports has been rising
OL,12,Fyear-on-year since the pandemic,
OL,13,Faccording to the RSPCA.
OL,15,FNationally, the charity received
OL,16,F52,662 reports in 2023, compared with
OL,17,F42,613 reports of cruelty to dogs in
OL,18,F2020 - a 23% increase in four years.
