OL,3,C'Shocking' rise in dog cruelty
OL,4,Creports, says RSPCA
OL,6,FMs Thompson said there's "a whole list
OL,7,Fof reasons" as to why the figures have
OL,8,Fbeen rising.
OL,10,F"I think Covid had a massive effect
OL,11,Fwhere people weren't able to report or
OL,12,Fsee cruelty anymore - so what we've
OL,13,Fseen is the knock on effect of that,
OL,14,Fand then also the cost of living
OL,15,Fcrisis," she said.
OL,17,FMs Thompson added there's "no excuse"
OL,18,Ffor treating animals badly.
