OL,3,C'Shocking' rise in dog cruelty
OL,4,Creports, says RSPCA
OL,6,FShe said: "We give out welfare
OL,7,Fassistance everyday to people that are
OL,8,Fstruggling with their veterinary
OL,9,Fbills, and we offer food.
OL,11,F"Other charities do incredible work to
OL,12,Fsupport people and their pets in the
OL,13,Fhome, so all people need to do is to
OL,14,Freach out and not turn to drastic
OL,15,Fmeasures and fail their animals."
OL,17,FThe new data has been released as part
OL,18,Fof the organisation's No Animal
OL,19,FDeserves Cruelty appeal, which aims
OL,20,Fencourage people to create a kinder
OL,21,Fworld for animals.
